msgstr "ein Ticket ist eskaliert"

#: ../system/integrations/slack.rst:28
msgid "a Ticket is going to escalate"
msgstr "ein Ticket ist kurz vorm Eskalieren"

#: ../system/integrations/slack.rst:30
msgid ""
"Zammad will provide the Ticket title, a direct link to the Ticket, the event "
